Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Aviation
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是少年飞翔了
